text.section:
Subject to approval by the Commission under subsection (c) of this section, after a claim has been filed by a covered employee or the dependents of a covered employee, the covered employee or dependents may enter into an agreement for the final compromise and settlement of any current or future claim under this title with:
the employer;
the insurer of the employer;
the Subsequent Injury Fund; or
the Uninsured Employers' Fund.
